## Performance Benchmarks ğŸ“Š

| Operation         | FletX | Pure Flet |
|-------------------|-------|-----------|
| State Update      | 0.2ms | 1.5ms     |
| Route Navigation  | 5ms   | 15ms      |
| DI Resolution     | 0.1ms | N/A       |

